<div class="modal fade" id="receiptCountsHelp" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="receiptCountsHelpLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg modal-dialog-scrollable">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title" id="receiptCountsHelpLabel">Receipt Counts Help</h5>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <p>This screen registers blind or assisted counts for inbound receipt items.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Mode</strong>: choose Blind to hide expected quantities or Assisted to display expected quantities.</li>
                    <li><strong>Inbound Order Item</strong>: select the item you are counting.</li>
                    <li><strong>Counted Quantity</strong>: enter the physical count (use decimals when needed).</li>
                    <li><strong>Variance</strong>: shows the difference between expected and counted quantities.</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Counts are stored per item, and divergences are highlighted for quick review.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
